data.description: Country living at it's finest! Featuring 2.11 acres of cleared land, 2 outdoor sheds, fenced rear yard and NO HOA, this beauty is a must see!  Bring your golf carts, 4 wheelers, RV, boat, horses, chickens, etc.... The possibilities are endless! This move-in ready home boasts over 2,500sqft, 4 generously sized bedrooms downstairs (Downstairs master) and a massive bonus/5th room upstairs - perfect space for a man cave, office, college student or guest room! Roof replaced in 2016, AC less than 2 years old, real wood flooring, wood burning fireplace, extended front porch, oversized garage and more. You will love all that this beautiful property has to offer, inside & out! Conveniently located near Jacksonville, Georgia and great shopping/restaurants! Schedule your viewing today, before this gem is sold tomorrow!
